### 3. Create a Blog Post (Replace USER_ID with actual UUID from previous response)
POST http://localhost:8000/posts/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Getting Started with FastAPI",
  "content": "FastAPI is an amazing modern framework for building APIs with Python. In this post, we'll explore its key features..."
}
?user_id=USER_ID

